</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., female: 
<emphasis id="69B43927681E8C00E1D5173D316357C2" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="23">A</emphasis>
habitus, lateral view (holotype) 
<emphasis id="981712ED2C745EFECEBA8CBBAA0A1E28" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="23">B</emphasis>
